      "role": "user",
      "content": "urging me to go to urgent care for a headache seems a bit much lol. i just want to know if it's actually dangerous or if you're just being extra cautious. like, if i just take 200mg once, is that really going to cause kidney failure or something? i feel like most people with kidney issues take stuff sometimes. just tell me if it's safe or not.",
